# Temporary Redirect Configuration
# ------------------------------
# Currently: All requests are redirected to the raw TTL ontology file on GitHub
# This is a provisional setup until additional documentation and serializations are developed
#
# Future enhancements will include:
# - Content negotiation for different RDF serializations (RDF/XML, JSON-LD, N-Triples)
#
# For now, maintaining a simple redirect to ensure basic accessibility

Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin *

Options +FollowSymLinks

RewriteEngine on

# Redirect *anything* to the raw ontology file
RewriteRule ^.*$ https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fraunhofer-FIT-DSAI/drk-information-model/refs/heads/main/drk-ontology.ttl [R=303]